rComments: Trudo gives amazing lectures. His passion for health law rubs off on you. Very popular with students. He is always willing to meet and help his students with potential paper topics or any issues they may be having. He genuinely wants his students to succeed. Lucky to have had him as a prof. Strongly recommend him to everyone interested in health.
The illusion: Medical Law might be useful and interesting. The reality: worst; entirely useless; tedious; surprisingly boring.
